high_descs: turn right and walk over to the bath tub on the left side corner of the room
grab a wash cloth out of the bath tub
turn right and walk over to the bathroom sink on the left
place the cloth inside of the bathroom sink, rinse it off, then take it back out
turn to the left a bit
place the cloth on top of the toilet there
anns.task_desc: place a clean cloth on top of the toilet

high_descs: Pick up the closest dirty black rag out of the tub.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the left sink.
Put the dirty rag in the left sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean rag.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn around to face the toilet.
Put the clean black rag on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean black rag on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn and go to the bathtub.
Pick up a rag in the bathtub.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the rag in the sink.
Turn and go to the toilet.
Put the rag on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed rag on the toilet.
